war.model

Class CsiroDataBaseline

  • java.lang.Object
    • war.model.CsiroDataBaseline

  • @Entity
public class CsiroDataBaseline
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing the baseline data from the dataset available from CSIRO. It associates values to the climate variables and climate parameters.
    Since:
    01th Feb. 2013
    Author:
    Guillaume Prevost
